file_content.text: Is it... is it done?
Please... turn this off. Let me go home....
Get back to Mos Ila. Find a medic.
You're free.
Th--thank you....
You don't deserve to live.
I don't reward failure.
Urk, argh! No! Don't leave me here...!
Uurrrgh....
Are you part of Captain Tremont's team?
W--what? Who are you? Did the captain send you? Everyone else is dead!
I don't know why they, hrph, kept me alive. I think they're... torture....
What's the situation?
Let me help you.
Would the Imperial military do any less to you for your failure?
That's what you deserve.
N--no... please. I'll be executed unless the mission... completed....
We never got, hrph, as far as the ammo stockyard. Ambushed.
They stripped our gear... explosives... in that locker.... Please... finish the job....
[There appears to be an unconscious Imperial soldier in this force cage.]
